OL,3,CBorder Force at Heathrow Airport to
OL,4,Cstage more strikes
OL,6,FHundreds of border force officers at
OL,7,Fare set to stage more strikes in a
OL,8,Fdispute over rosters.
OL,10,FMore than 500 members of The Public
OL,11,Fand Commercial Services union will
OL,12,Fwalk out on May 31, June 1 and 2.
OL,14,FIt will be followed by three weeks of
OL,15,Faction short of a strike including
OL,16,Fstaff refusing to work overtime from
OL,17,FJune 4.
OL,19,FThe officers, who work in terminals 2,
OL,20,F3, 4 and 5, took four days of action
OL,21,Flast month.
