OL,4,Cstage more strikes
OL,6,FPCS general secretary Fran Heathcote
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are keen to resolve this
OL,8,Fdispute but the Home Office must first
OL,9,Fput something on the table for our
OL,10,Fmembers to consider.
OL,12,F"The Home Office has said it is 'open
OL,13,Fto discuss' a resolution but it only
OL,14,Fresponded to our request for a meeting
OL,15,Fafter we threatened further action.
OL,17,F"Until it comes back with changes to
OL,18,Fthe roster that will benefit our
OL,19,Fmembers then the dispute will
OL,20,Fcontinue."
